DISCLOSURE; GOVERNMENT REGULATION; TEACHERS -- CALIFORNIA; ASSAULTS -- 
CALIFORNIA; STUDENTS -- CALIFORNIA; CAPITAL PUNISHMENT -- CALIFORNIA; FAST FOOD 
INDUSTRY -- CALIFORNIA; LABELS 
</P>
