<P>
Photo, Barrier falls -- Hungarian Foreign Minister Gyula Horn, right, and his 
Austrian counter-part, Alois Mock, snip barbed wire to bring down the last of 
the "iron curtin" between their two countries. Hungary began dismantling the 
fence last month as a gesture of good will. Reuters 
</P>
