<P>
Susan Sullivan, who has starred as Maggie Channing on CBS' "Falcon Crest" since 
1981, will leave the nest sometime after the series begins its ninth season 
this fall, Lorimar Television President David E. Salzman announced Tuesday. 
"I've been with the show since the beginning and I feel the character has run 
its course," Sullivan said in a news release. "It feels like leaving home." 
