-- TRADE; HONG KONG -- GOVERNMENT; CHINA -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- HONG KONG; 
REUNIFICATION; CHINA -- GOVERNMENT; CHINA -- REVOLTS; FORECASTS 
</P>
