A college student has lost a bid to collect a $1.1-million casino jackpot he 
hit while gambling illegally as a 19-year-old. 
</P>
<P>
State District Judge Donald Mosley Tuesday upheld a ruling by state gaming 
regulators allowing Caesars Palace to refuse to pay Kirk Erickson, now 21, of 
